cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.RO 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper proposes a visual tracking framework. 
2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper proposes a pre-event method for selecting experts based on past performance. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another likely category as the paper mentions using multiple component trackers and result ensemble. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper deals with tracking objects in videos. 
5. cs.RO (Robotics) is also a possible category as the proposed tracking framework can be applied to robotic vision systems.
